            <dd>I don&apos;t know. Better this than stupid ape JPEGs, I guess.</dd>
            
            <dt><a href="https://www.youtube.com/c/CleoAbram">HUGE *if true</a></dt>
            <dd>Cleo Abram, formerly of Vox, has gone the way of independent YouTube journalist. Her new series, "HUGE *if true", covers controversial tech from an exploratory angle.</dd>
            
            <dt><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ben9qDbrLYU">Music Pick: "Chaeri" by Magdalena Bay</a></dt>
            <dd>A catchy tune from the band's <cite>Mercurial World</cite> album, which I have been really enjoying lately. Full of hooks, with a sticky, pulsing bass line, and some excellent textures layered in as the track progresses. A lot of mornings lately, I wake up and this is the first thing I want to hear.</dd>
